Hamilton was released on Disney+ on July 3, 2020. Due to the COVID-19 pandemic and the closure of theaters, Disney+ acquired the rights to the original Broadway production of Hamilton, and released it on their streaming platform. The filmed version of the production was directed by Thomas Kail, who also directed the stage production, and features the original cast, including Lin-Manuel Miranda, Leslie Odom Jr., Phillipa Soo, and Daveed Diggs.